.center-block.mw600(ng-if="!vm.committee.name")
    .text-center.mb30
        img.mb20(src="/images/committee-icons/committees.png")
        div.fs20 Liazon Committees
    p The Liazon Celebration &amp; Service Committee's mission is focused around three core components:
    ul
        li Employee Recognition and Engagement
        li Community Outreach and Volunteerism
        li Team Building
    p The Celebration &amp; Service Committee is comprised of the following 4 sub-committees:
    .row
        .col-md-6
            a.boxed-link.text-center(ui-sref="committees.fun-games")
                img(ng-src="/images/committee-icons/fun-games.svg")
                h4 Fun &amp Games Committee
        .col-md-6
            a.boxed-link.text-center(ui-sref="committees.diversity")
                img(ng-src="/images/committee-icons/diversity.svg")
                h4 Cultural Diversity &amp; Community Outreach Committee
    .row
        .col-md-6
            a.boxed-link.text-center(ui-sref="committees.wellness")
                img(ng-src="/images/committee-icons/wellness.svg")
                h4 Wellness Committee
        .col-md-6
            a.boxed-link.text-center(ui-sref="committees.beautification")
                img(ng-src="/images/committee-icons/beautification.svg")
                h4 Beautification Committee

.center-block.committee(ng-if="vm.committee.name")
    .text-center.committee-header.mb30
        img.mb20(ng-src="/images/committee-icons/{{::vm.committee.name}}.svg")
        div.fs20
            span {{::vm.committee.text}} Committee
    p(ng-if="vm.committee.name === 'fun-games'") The Fun &amp; Games committee is dedicated to creating fun and interesting activities and events for everyone in the office to participate in. Examples: bubble hockey tournament, summer picnic, fantasy sports leagues, discount programs at local businesses etc.
    p(ng-if="vm.committee.name === 'diversity'") The Cultural Diversity and Community Outreach committee is dedicated to working on engaging the workforce in cultural diversity awareness. Identifying Cultural community events, working on ethnic heritage months etc.
    p(ng-if="vm.committee.name === 'wellness'") The Wellness committee is dedicated to creating programs that will make healthy choices easier. Examples: bike sharing program, biggest loser contest, destination walking program, healthy cookbook.
    p(ng-if="vm.committee.name === 'beautification'") The Beautification committee is dedicated to working on the beautification of the inside and the outside of the new office! Examples: naming of the conference rooms, plants, flowers, artwork throughout the office etc.
    h3.mv30.fw400.text-center Members
    ul.text-center.committee-members(vertilize-container)
        li(ng-repeat="member in vm.committeeMembers", ng-click="vm.profileEmployee(member)", vertilize, page="org-chart")
            img(ng-src="/images/employee-photos/{{member.image}}", ng-show="member.image")
            span.fa.fa-user.fs70(ng-hide="member.image")
            h5 {{member.displayName}}
            h6 {{member.title}}
